One-Wave / Four-Interaction Theory

«One field. Four interactions. Not four forces.»

Purpose

This repository is an audit trail for the One-Wave framework.

The goal is to separate:

- Definitions
- Proven results
- Proof candidates
- Working interpretations
- Experiments
- Redo paths

Nothing is promoted without explicit derivation, experiment, or gate closure.

The document's job is to keep the cracks visible.

The theory's job is to close them one at a time.

